entries.title_d: The Tusk Cat Run is a series of small smuggling assignments using droid controlled delivery and attack drones.
entries.title: Corellia System: Tusk Cat Run - Final Leg
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: Travel to the specified location and await the arrival of the delivery drone.
entries.quest_location_d: The next delivery takes place in the Naboo system.
entries.quest_dock2_d: Move in close to the delivery drone and use the /dock command to deliver package eight and end the Tusk Cat Run.
entries.found_loc_d: Navigation waypoint loaded. Meet delivery drone here.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: Transfer complete. Package eight secure. Tusk Cat Run complete.
entries.autorewardbody: Congratulations on completing the Tusk Cat Run. A bonus award of 8000 credits is being transferred to your account!
entries.attack_stopped: Tusk Cat Run: < Attack drones destroyed >
entries.attack_notify: Tusk Cat Run: < Attack drones incoming >
